item.title: CVE-2017-1002010|2024-08-05T22:00:41.651Z -- ontraport -- membership%20simplified
item.description: Vulnerability in wordpress plugin Membership Simplified v1.58, The code in membership-simplified-for-oap-members-only/updateDB.php is vulnerable to blind SQL injection because it doesn't sanitize user input via recordId in the delete_media function.
